name: Tick Tock Goes My Clock!
description: Welcome back! Foundation- "an underlying basis or principle" does this apply to you? With your 15% commission fees? Your 400/500 dollar mint/sale fees? Only allowing artists to invite other artist after they sell a piece? The wasteland known as Foundation app, I implore to all artists, this is not for you, this is for the fat cats, the collectors and site owners, to line their pockets. This has nothing to do with art! This is not about me this is about us, the 1s and 0s. Who am I? I am 101!
